Package: DynamicGP
Title: Modelling and Analysis of Dynamic Computer Experiments
Version: 1.1-9
Description: Emulating and solving inverse problems for dynamic
        computer experiments. It contains two major functionalities:
        (1) localized GP model for large-scale dynamic computer
        experiments using the algorithm proposed by Zhang et al. (2018)
        <arXiv:1611.09488>; (2) solving inverse problems in dynamic
        computer experiments. The current version only supports 64-bit
        version of R.
